name: Siku Quanshu Online
description: The Siku Quanshu (Wenyuange Edition), compiled in 1773-1782 by edict from Emperor Qianlong, contains 3,460 works on topics including history, politics, economics, and more. Note: For now, you must use MS Internet Explorer, not Firefox to access this. After downloading the installation package, you will need to select the log in by IP option. **Only available on NYUNET.
